{"tid":245612,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"中樂樂器分享區（膀頭有花既入曬黎）","createTime":"2017-05-16T11:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T08:36:44.000Z","uid":8460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f0822bf057e32e5be31a46a20025dfe85de02e44","tid":245612,"uid":8460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"純粹想睇下連登有幾多巴絲有玩開中樂，可以分享下為何中意該種樂器、如何結緣、年資、有咩特別既演奏技巧等等...<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉先，在下吹笛子，亦偶爾會撫撫琴，都係一知半解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，中學開始接觸，畢業後當興趣得閒玩下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n國術大師快快進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"419fea61dec0abf9b631c8c13aa00e6df5576647","tid":245612,"uid":19727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"玩過柳琴，玩左一年就無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時中學見學校有得學先玩下<br />\n但中六太忙無咩時間所以就無再掂"},{"pid":"1300f8ff894d3c0b864359d34d1b9f5a6f268401","tid":245612,"uid":8460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩過柳琴，玩左一年就無玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個時中學見學校有得學先玩下<br />\n但中六太忙無咩時間所以就無再掂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n終於有第一個中樂撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n柳琴正啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前街頭睇過人用琵琶配柳琴合奏表演，一流"},{"pid":"b912148fa4827283a7d8ca022d884f14c17ebf48","tid":245612,"uid":108595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T02:59:06.000Z","msg":"二胡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過已經近10年無拉，因為太忙"},{"pid":"c403f84b8a75e64e78504e49bab84e8418c1deeb","tid":245612,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"柳琴+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576e330fb89466d575564c75729f5a8a93609257","tid":245612,"uid":8460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二胡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過已經近10年無拉，因為太忙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實一直都想學下拉二胡，拉起黎有一種好淒美既感覺 btw 一副二胡粵華行六百幾七百有交易，但究竟難唔難入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efeda35d1d655cfe8c3ff89f4d4e25c32aa01d9","tid":245612,"uid":45479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"敲擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 古箏就學過幾年<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae534dae10e71f236adc298ef1c2caaa11231c34","tid":245612,"uid":94337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T08:36:44.000Z","msg":"古琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學左差唔多半年多d<br />\n彈到手指痛"}]}